topic: GDP at Current Prices and Real GDP
question_en: What is the difference between GDP at Current Prices and Real GDP?
question_hi: गीत्रीय मान के आधार पर GDP (वर्षीय मान के आधार पर) और Real GDP के अर्थ कैसे वाले रंग हैं?

options.option_text: GDP at Current Prices is the total value of goods and services produced in a year in a country's economy, while Real GDP is the GDP adjusted for inflation.
